product.title: Personalized Patriotic V-Neck Tee, Custom Name Shirt, 4th of July Top, Memorial Day Outfit, Americana Graphic Tee
product.description:
Introducing a versatile Unisex Jersey Short Sleeve V-Neck Tee that radiates comfort and style. This tee combines a casual aesthetic with a trendy silhouette, making it ideal for both laid-back days and semi-formal occasions. The lightweight cotton fabric ensures breathability, perfect for warm weather or layering in cooler seasons. Designed for adults, it’s great for anyone wanting to express their individual style comfortably. Celebrate special moments like birthdays, holidays, and gatherings while enjoying a piece that effortlessly fits into both everyday wear and festive celebrations!

Product features
- Designed with side seams for enhanced shape retention and structural support
- Features a ribbed knit collar that maintains its elasticity and shape
- Shoulder tape stabilizes the back, preventing stretching
- Made from lightweight 100% cotton for a smooth, comfortable experience
- Produced by Bella+Canvas under Fair Labor Association standards, ensuring humane and sustainable practices

Care instructions
- Do not dryclean
- Machine wash: warm (max 40C or 105F)
- Non-chlorine: bleach as needed
- Tumble dry: low heat
- Iron, steam or dry: medium heat
